de_incido_v7
A prodigy bunker style map with two bombspots and 70 Player starts.
In this version improved balance and performance.
Bots are pretty dumb since I couldnt create a new nav.file. (source update)
Tested with 64 players and it worked pretty well, balance and fps-wise.

I know this is no masterpiece but I did what I could with the time I have :)

Radarmap and nav. file are included in the bsp.
I hope you enjoy playing it :)

wostok
